-- Home Retail First-Half Sales Decline 3% as It Maintains Interim Dividend
-- B y   J e r r o l d   C o l t e n
-- 2010-10-20T06:03:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/home-retail-first-half-sales-decline-3-as-it-maintains-interim-dividend.html
Home Retail Group Plc said in a
statement today that first-half sales fell 3 percent to 2.72
billion pounds and the company maintained its interim dividend
at 4.7 pence.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
